   Date:  Sun, 27 Apr 1997 23:35:07 -0600
  Files:  hints/hpux.sh

  Title:  "Win32 update (three patches)"
   From:  Gurusamy Sarathy and Nick Ing-Simmons
  Files:  win32/makedef.pl win32/perllib.c win32/win32.c

