   From:  Hallvard B Furuseth and Chip Salzenberg
  Files:  perlsdio.h pp_sys.c

  Title:  "Fix typo in NeXT dynaloader"
   From:  Chip Salzenberg
  Files:  ext/DynaLoader/dl_next.xs

  Title:  "Fix possible buffer overflow under VMS"
   From:  Chip Salzenberg
  Files:  taint.c

