          (Add 'require IO::Handle' at beginning of FileHandle.pm)
   From:  Chip Salzenberg
  Files:  ext/FileHandle/FileHandle.pm

  Title:  "Re: strtod / strtol patch for POSIX module"
   From:  hammen@gothamcity.jsc.nasa.gov (David Hammen)
