Index: lib/Pod/Text.pm

    Date: Fri, 20 Sep 1996 15:08:33 +0100 (BST)
    From: "Joseph S. Myers" <jsm28@hermes.cam.ac.uk>
    Subject: Pod typos, pod2man bugs, and miscellaneous installation comments

